mapview::mapview(spatial_rj_neighborhoods %>% dplyr::filter(lon < -30), 
                 map = leaflet::leaflet() %>% leaflet::addTiles(),
                 zcol="cases", cex="cases",
                 layer.name="Casos",
                 label=paste0(spatial_rj_neighborhoods$neighborhood, ": ",
                              spatial_rj_neighborhoods$cases))
